  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to generate and valid a co-morbidity score with updated
      definitions and suitable for use in Argentina in both public and private settings. These
      tools would allow us to compare different populations in Argentina adjusting for
      comorbidities. Also, this would potentially help attending physicians and health
      administrators.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will generate a co-morbidity score, perform the score validation and
      generate an online calculator for the score (open access).

      Finally, a score validation for extreme values of score will be performed to ensure
      representativeness of these patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
